    <div class="flex-about-page">
      <p>We are Somya and Youness, a happy French-Moroccan married couple. <br><br>
      After working hard for almost 6 years in the tech ecosystem, me (Somya) as an E-store specialist and
      Youness as a Customer success manager, we've decided to live our dream, <b>explore Asia</b>. <br>
      Unpredictable by nature, we've packed our bags and went through this journey to the unknown for the next 6 months. <br><br>
      We've tasted genuine freedom, from the marvellous Ninh Binh valley to the ancient temples of Angkor Wat
      and the majestic Mount Fuji. <br> We've explored <b>10 countries</b> from the Far East to the Middle East,
      experimenting unique cultures, flavorful cuisines and deep connections with amazing locals. <br><br>
      We wanted to share
      our tips with you in a simple way for you to follow, that's why we've created <b>Tou-do-rist</b>, the To-Do lists
      for the tourists, to regroup all the must dos we advice you to experience in these locations : Vietnam, Indonesia,
      Thailand, The Philippines, South-Korea, Japan, Cambodia, Malaysia, UAE and Saudi Arabia!
      We really hope you'll appreciate our tips !
